    Class Description
    AdListener
    A Phunware ad listener to listen for ad events.

    An Phunware SDK ad request used to load an ad.
    AdSize
    The size (width and height) of an ad request.
    BannerView
    The fragment extension containing a Banner.
    Beacon
    Models a beacon from a Placement.
    InterstitialView
    An Interstitial object, which can be displayed once.
    Phunware
    Makes requests against the Phunware API.
    Placement
    Models the Placement with all its properties.
    PlacementRequest

    PlacementResponse
    Holds the response status and list of placements.
    Positions
    Positions where a banner ad can be placed on screen.
